 <h3>A Prelude</h3>
<div class="normal"> <p>We are a leading manufacturing and wholesale silver jewelry organization. Under the decorous leadership of Mr. Gopal Butani (Patel), who ignited our business more than two decades ago in the field of specific Jewelry at Gujarat and gradually he developed and discovered his own art and new angle in jewelry, which resulted in a new dimension in fashion world and became synonyms of Fashion Jewelry. </p>

<p>Over a Period of time after thorough knowledge transformation about silver jewelry to Mr.Ashish Suvagiya and Mr.jayant Babariya who joined hands with him which took the business to greater heights.</p>

<h3>A Breif About Us</h3>
<p>Since the inception of our company, at Kovai Silver, we have made an indelible mark in the minds of our customers influencing the latest trends in the prevailing Silver Jewelry market exclusively. The mesmerizing range of jewelry that we manufacture and trade comprises of Payal, Chain, Metti, Ferva, Ladies & Gents Key chain, Bracelet, Bangle, Ring, Pendant, Stud, All types of Vessels and many more. We use both traditional and latest methods of manufacturing array of jewelry. It is always taken into consideration that the quality of the raw materials that we use is of the highest grade. Hence stringent checks are done before these materials are brought into our production unit. After due penetration into the market, we have extended our arms further by incorporating our unit to a wider one, named, Kovai Silver (P) Ltd, an organization with predefined missions and visions. It has been possible to bring out such an amazing range of products with the help of our skillful craftsmen and designers. The brilliance of their designs is evident in our finished jewelry products, which is visible on the amount of satisfied customers we have in the market. Moreover we have priced the products very reasonably, which further attracts bulk buyers in reaching us.
</p>

<h3>Our Spectrum of Products</h3>
<p>The array of our products like Bangles, Chains, Bracelets and rings are finely crafted to bring the brilliant designs to life. We use only that material which has been approved by our quality checking staffs in the initial stages of sourcing. Our beaded Metti, Bangles & Fervas etc., has a mass appeal as their designs keep changing according to the changing fashion trends. The magnitude of our products is renowned for its beauty, rarity, fashion, durability and individual tastes.</p>

<h3>Our Infrastructure</h3>
<p>Our production unit is equipped with a state-of-the-art infrastructure which is a perfect example of a blend of modern and traditional techniques. Each batch of our jewelry items undergoes protocols like Cutting, Polishing, Coating, Packing, and Bar-coding. Kovai Silver gives you the assurance of providing any sort of Silver requirements, in short “All under one roof and we strive to keep up “There is no better place to experience Silver”</p>

<h3>Quality Credibility</h3>
<p>Apart from latest designs of jewelry their quality is of utmost importance to us. Adhering to set quality standards has become a habit for our company. Hence we have a vigilant quality team whose job is to ensure we deal with only flawless products. We strongly believe in “Checking products at every stage of production ensures minimal flaws in the final outcome”. Moreover we have our own Quality Check instrument wherein customers can check the purity level of their old silver by themselves which they interchange for purchase of new items from us, which would enable them, understand the product better.</p>

<h3>Our Clients</h3>
<p>Under no circumstances we let the quality of our products suffer and such assurances by us have strengthened the trust that our customers have on us. Our prima facie customers are basically Wholesale Buyers, who are the backbone of the prevailing market. Currently we concentrate on Quality Manufacturing and wholesale trading. Wide spread market has enormous traders and one can think on why do we need to deal with Kovai Silver.</p>

